            <a href="#termination" class="toc-link block px-3 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-zinc-400 hover:bg-rose-50/50 dark:hover:bg-rose-500/10 hover:text-[#FF385C] dark:hover:text-[#FF385C] transition border-l-4 border-transparent pl-3">7. Account Termination</a>
